Feats (challenges)
------------------
sneak	Only attack and kill with stabs.
frugal	Use only one weapon throughout the game.

Movement patterns
-----------------
sneak	[move, move, rest, move]
charge	[move(A), move(A), move(A), attack(A)]
lunge	[move(A), move(A), attack(A)] (dagger)

